text: Clyde Kirby Wells, (born November 9, 1937) is a Canadian politician. He was the fifth Premier of Newfoundland and Labrador from 1989 to 1996. He was the Chief Justice of Newfoundland and Labrador, sitting on the Supreme Court of Newfoundland and Labrador (Court of Appeal) from 1998 to 2009. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Premiers of Newfoundland and Labrador Category:Canadian King's Counsel
